South Africa May Access BlackBerry Messages, TechCentral Says

-- B y   R e n e e   B o n o r c h i s
-- 
2011-09-06T05:24:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-06/south-africa-calls-for-law-to-access-blackberry-messages-techcentral-says.html
South Africa  may change legislation
to allow law enforcers access to BlackBerry Messenger services,
TechCentral said, citing Communications Deputy Minister Obed
Bapela.  Government wants access to a decryption system if crimes
are committed using the BlackBerry service, the Johannesburg-
based online news site said, quoting Bapela.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Renee Bonorchis at 
 rbonorchis@bloomberg.net  